{"nodes":[{"pos":[12,49],"content":"Compiler Error C2141 | Microsoft Docs","needQuote":false,"needEscape":true,"nodes":[{"content":"Compiler Error C2141 | Microsoft Docs","pos":[0,37]}]},{"pos":[597,617],"content":"Compiler Error C2141","linkify":"Compiler Error C2141","nodes":[{"content":"Compiler Error C2141","pos":[0,20]}]},{"content":"array size overflow","pos":[618,637]},{"content":"An array exceeds the 2GB limit.","pos":[644,675]},{"content":"Reduce the size of the array.","pos":[676,705]},{"pos":[714,721],"content":"Example","linkify":"Example","nodes":[{"content":"Example","pos":[0,7]}]},{"content":"The following sample generates C2141.","pos":[725,762]}],"content":"---\ntitle: \"Compiler Error C2141 | Microsoft Docs\"\nms.custom: \"\"\nms.date: \"11/04/2016\"\nms.reviewer: \"\"\nms.suite: \"\"\nms.technology: \n  - \"devlang-cpp\"\nms.tgt_pltfrm: \"\"\nms.topic: \"error-reference\"\nf1_keywords: \n  - \"C2141\"\ndev_langs: \n  - \"C++\"\nhelpviewer_keywords: \n  - \"C2141\"\nms.assetid: 10cf770f-0500-4220-ac90-a863b7ea5fe6\ncaps.latest.revision: 4\nauthor: \"corob-msft\"\nms.author: \"corob\"\nmanager: \"ghogen\"\ntranslation.priority.ht: \n  - \"cs-cz\"\n  - \"de-de\"\n  - \"es-es\"\n  - \"fr-fr\"\n  - \"it-it\"\n  - \"ja-jp\"\n  - \"ko-kr\"\n  - \"pl-pl\"\n  - \"pt-br\"\n  - \"ru-ru\"\n  - \"tr-tr\"\n  - \"zh-cn\"\n  - \"zh-tw\"\n---\n# Compiler Error C2141\narray size overflow  \n  \n An array exceeds the 2GB limit. Reduce the size of the array.  \n  \n## Example  \n The following sample generates C2141.  \n  \n```  \n// C2141.cpp  \n// processor: IPF  \nclass A {  \n   short m_n;  \n};  \n  \nint main()  \n{  \n   A* pA = (A*)(-1);  \n   pA = new A[0x8000000000000001];   // C2141  \n  \n   A* pA2 = (A*)(-1);  \n   pA2 = new A[0x80000000000000F];   // OK  \n}  \n```"}